<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>홍채촬영 | IRIS MAPPING LAB</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css?v=20260623-shooting-guide-1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="site-navigation.css?v=20260623-072747">
</head>
<body>
  <section id="authScreen" class="auth-screen">
    <div class="auth-card">
      <div class="auth-brand" hidden>
        <span class="auth-logo" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <strong>IRIS MAPPING LAB</strong>
      </div>

      <div class="auth-title">
        <h1>눈동자 상세 맵핑</h1>
        <p>홍채 분석을 통한 건강 인사이트</p>
      </div>

      <div class="auth-hero" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <p class="auth-quote">“눈동자는 마음의 창이자<br>신체의 지도를 담고 있습니다.”</p>

      <div class="auth-panel">
        <h2>로그인</h2>
        <p class="auth-copy">이름과 전화번호로 분석을 시작하세요.</p>

        <form id="loginForm" class="auth-form">
          <label>이름 <input id="loginName" type="text" autocomplete="name" placeholder="이름" required></label>
          <label>전화번호 <input id="loginPhone" type="tel" autocomplete="tel" placeholder="전화번호" required></label>
          <button class="primary" type="submit">로그인</button>
        </form>

        <div class="auth-divider"><span>또는</span></div>

        <form id="signupForm" class="auth-form signup-form">
          <label>이름 <input id="signupName" type="text" autocomplete="name" placeholder="이름" required></label>
          <label>전화번호 <input id="signupPhone" type="tel" autocomplete="tel" placeholder="전화번호" required></label>
          <label>이메일 <input id="signupEmail" type="email" autocomplete="email" placeholder="이메일"></label>
          <label>주소 <input id="signupAddress" type="text" autocomplete="street-address" placeholder="주소"></label>
          <label>추천인 <input id="signupReferrer" type="text" placeholder="추천인"></label>
          <button type="submit">회원가입</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <p id="authMessage" class="auth-message" role="status"></p>

      <footer class="auth-footer">
        <strong>IRIS MAPPING LAB</strong>
        <span>본 서비스는 의료 진단을 대체하지 않으며, 전문가 상담과 함께 활용하시기 바랍니다.</span>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main id="appShell" class="app-shell" hidden>
    <section class="workspace">
      <header class="topbar">
        <div class="actions">
          <label class="file-button primary">
            <input id="pairInput" type="file" accept="image/*" multiple>
            홍채사진 올리기
          </label>
          <button id="exportButton" type="button" disabled>판독하기</button>
          <input id="chartInput" type="file" accept="image/*" hidden>
          <button id="mappingButton" type="button" hidden>구독하기</button>
          <button id="universeButton" type="button" hidden>유니버스</button>
          <button id="logoutButton" type="button" hidden>로그아웃</button>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="canvas-wrap">
        <canvas id="irisCanvas" width="1280" height="360"></canvas>
        <div id="emptyState" class="empty-state">
          <strong>좌우 홍채 사진 2장을 올려주세요</strong>
          <span>사진을 올린 뒤 원형 프레임 안에서 드래그와 확대/축소로 홍채 위치를 맞춰주세요.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section id="irisPersonalDashboard" class="iris-personal-dashboard" aria-live="polite" hidden>
        <article class="iris-analysis-hero">
          <div class="iris-analysis-hero-copy">
            <span class="result-eyebrow">PERSONAL IRIS REPORT</span>
            <h2>홍채 종합 분석</h2>
            <p id="irisAnalysisLead">저장된 홍채 판독과 문진을 불러오는 중입니다.</p>
            <div id="irisAnalysisMeta" class="iris-analysis-meta"></div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="iris-result-card iris-top-card">
          <div class="iris-result-heading"><span>01</span><h2>상위 관리 영역 TOP5</h2></div>
          <div id="irisTopAreas" class="iris-top-areas"></div>
        </article>

        <article class="iris-result-card">
          <div class="iris-result-heading"><span>02</span><h2>문진 교차확인 결과</h2></div>
          <div id="irisQuestionnaireCrosscheck" class="iris-result-content"></div>
        </article>

        <article class="iris-result-card">
          <div class="iris-result-heading"><span>03</span><h2>종합 해석</h2></div>
          <div id="irisIntegratedSummary" class="iris-result-content"></div>
        </article>

        <article class="iris-result-card">
          <div class="iris-result-heading"><span>04</span><h2>추천 관리 방향</h2></div>
          <div id="irisManagementDirections" class="iris-result-content"></div>
        </article>

        <article class="iris-result-card iris-shopping-card">
          <div class="iris-result-heading"><span>05</span><h2>쇼핑 추천</h2></div>
          <div id="irisShoppingRecommendations" class="iris-result-content"></div>
          <a class="iris-result-link" href="shopping.html">추천 이유와 성분 자세히 보기</a>
        </article>
      </section>
    </section>

    <aside class="side-panel">
      <section class="panel-block shooting-guide-panel">
        <h2>홍채 촬영 방법</h2>
        <p>촬영 전 아래 안내를 보고 좌안과 우안 사진을 선명하게 촬영해주세요.</p>
        <img class="shooting-guide-image" src="assets/iris-shooting-guide.png" alt="홍채 촬영 방법 안내">
      </section>

      <section class="panel-block">
        <h2>촬영 위치 맞추기</h2>
        <p class="alignment-guide-copy">원 안의 사진을 드래그하고 확대/축소해서 동공 중심을 가운데에 맞춰주세요.</p>
        <label class="control" hidden>중심 X
          <input id="centerX" type="range" min="0" max="640" value="320" disabled>
        </label>
        <label class="control" hidden>중심 Y
          <input id="centerY" type="range" min="0" max="360" value="180" disabled>
        </label>
        <label class="control" hidden>동공 반지름
          <input id="pupilRadius" type="range" min="10" max="140" value="54" disabled>
        </label>
        <label class="control" hidden>홍채 반지름
          <input id="irisRadius" type="range" min="40" max="180" value="118" disabled>
        </label>
        <label class="control" hidden>12시 방향 회전
          <input id="overlayRotation" type="range" min="-30" max="30" step="1" value="0" disabled>
        </label>
        <div id="alignmentStatus" class="alignment-status" aria-live="polite"></div>
        <button id="centerResetButton" type="button" disabled hidden>정렬 다시 시작</button>
        <button id="alignmentSaveButton" class="primary" type="button" disabled>정렬 저장</button>
        <button id="autoDetectButton" type="button" disabled>맵핑하기</button>
      </section>

      <div class="legacy-output">
        <div class="reference-preview">
          <img id="chartPreview" alt="기준 홍채사진 보기">
          <span id="chartEmpty">기준 홍채사진 없음</span>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-grid">
          <button class="photo-card active" type="button" data-eye="right">
            <span class="photo-title">우안</span>
            <span id="rightPhotoName" class="photo-name">사진 없음</span>
          </button>
          <button class="photo-card" type="button" data-eye="left">
            <span class="photo-title">좌안</span>
            <span id="leftPhotoName" class="photo-name">사진 없음</span>
          </button>
        </div>
        <button id="swapEyesButton" type="button" disabled>좌우 배정 바꾸기</button>
        <div id="selectionDetails"></div>
        <div id="detailMap"></div>
        <div id="markerList"></div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </main>

  <script src="iris-organ-db.js"></script>
  <script src="care-engine.js"></script>
  <script src="integrated-reading-engine.js"></script>
  <script src="app.js?v=20260623-round-frame-map-1"></script>
  <script src="iris-dashboard.js"></script>
  <script src="site-navigation.js?v=20260623-073145"></script>
</body>
</html>
